            <scopecontent id="aspace_fc3047f5bab4d7c2c992fc89341c2b94">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>KEEP FAMILY is composed primarily of the papers of Robert Porter Keep, which are arranged together at the beginning of the series. Where the correspondence with an individual is particularly full (a folder or more) these letters have been organized by the name of the individual. Smaller quantities of correspondence with individuals are arranged together in chronological order. At the end of the series are a few letters of other Keep family members, not to or from Robert Porter Keep. These are arranged in chronological order.</p>
            </scopecontent>
