               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>HAINES FAMILY is composed almost entirely of the correspondence of Margaret Haines Keep. Her major correspondent is her sister, Lillian M. Haines, and all letters between the sisters are arranged together at the beginning of the series. These are followed by Margaret Haines Keep's correspondence with a number of people, arranged together in chronological order, The last folder contains a few miscellaneous letters of other Haines family members, not to or from Margaret Haines Keep.</p>
